/products/oak-step-plus-op101-houston-plus/">View details</a><a class="button-inline ghost-inline" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&product=Oak%20Step%20PLUS%20OP101%20Houston%20PLUS&productSlug=oak-step-plus-op101-houston-plus&range=Oak%20Step%20PLUS&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Check stock</a></div></div></article></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Before ordering</p><h2>What to confirm before ordering laminate flooring</h2></div><p>Confirming these details early helps keep product choice, preparation and installation expectations clear.</p></div><div class="caution-grid"><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Check</span><h3>Dry internal suitability</h3><p>Confirm the room and cleaning routine suit the selected laminate product.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Review</span><h3>Subfloor flatness</h3><p>Check the floor base before installation so boards sit correctly.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Plan</span><h3>Moisture and cleaning conditions</h3><p>Review moisture exposure and cleaning expectations before choosing the range.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Confirm</span><h3>Stock, trims and transitions</h3><p>Confirm stock, trims, doorway transitions and adjoining floor heights.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Installation</p><h2>Need laminate flooring installed?</h2></div><p>Send your suburb, approximate floor area, current floor type, preferred range or colour, and any photos or floor plans. Oz Timber Floor can review product suitability, preparation and installation scope.</p></div><div class="fit-grid"><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Install</span><h3>Supply + install</h3><p>Connect range selection with installation scope and timing.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Prepare</span><h3>Floor preparation</h3><p>Check flatness and substrate condition before installation.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Access</span><h3>Access and timing</h3><p>Discuss parking, lifts, occupied rooms and project timing.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Finish</span><h3>Trims and transitions</h3><p>Plan trims, doorways, skirting or scotia before ordering.</p></article></div><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Request supply + install quote</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&topic=photos%20or%20floor%20plan&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Send photos / floor plan</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=service&topic=preparation&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Ask about preparation</a></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Related pages</p><h2>Plan the next step</h2></div><p>Use these pages to connect product choice with preparation, installation and project planning.</p></div><div class="grid-4"><a class="category-card link-card" href="/hybrid-flooring-sydney/"><strong>Hybrid flooring</strong><p>Compare laminate with hybrid flooring options.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="category-card link-card" href="/floor-levelling-sydney/"><strong>Floor levelling</strong><p>Prepare the subfloor before floating floor installation.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="category-card link-card" href="/timber-flooring-installation-sydney/"><strong>Timber flooring installation</strong><p>Plan installation details for the selected range.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="category-card link-card" href="/projects/"><strong>Projects</strong><p>See common flooring project examples.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class="section soft" id="faqs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">FAQs</p><h2>Common questions</h2></div><p>These answers help prepare a useful enquiry before product selection or installation planning.</p></div><div class="faq-list"><article class="faq-item"><button type="button">Is laminate suitable for kitchens or wet areas?</button><p>Some laminate ranges are designed with improved water resistance, but suitability depends on the exact product, room use and installation requirements. Ask before ordering for kitchens or moisture-prone spaces.</p></article><article class="faq-item"><button type="button">Can I request laminate supply only?</button><p>Yes. Send the range, colour, quantity or square metres and suburb so Oz can discuss supply price, availability and alternatives.</p></article><article class="faq-item"><button type="button">Does laminate need floor levelling?</button><p>Laminate needs a suitably flat and stable substrate. Uneven floors can affect the locking system, feel underfoot and long-term performance.</p></article><article class="faq-item"><button type="button">Can laminate be used in apartments?</button><p>Often, but acoustic underlay, strata rules, lift access, working hours and waste handling should be confirmed before installation.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Talk to Oz Timber Floor</p><h2>Ready to check a laminate flooring range?</h2><p>Send the range or colour, square metres, suburb, current floor type and whether you need supply-only, stock check, preparation or installation.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button-light" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-light" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Request supply price</a><a class="button-light" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&category=Laminate&source=laminate-flooring-sydney">Request supply + install quote</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="shell footer-grid"><div><img class="footer-brand-logo" src="/assets/brand/oz-timber-floor-logo.webp" alt="Oz Timber Floor" width="680" height="215"><p>Sydney timber flooring supplier, installer, builder flooring contractor and floor preparation specialist.</p></div><div><h3>Services</h3><div class="footer-links"><a href="/timber-flooring-installation-sydney/">Installation</a><a href="/floor-levelling-sydney/">Floor levelling</a><a href="/commercial-flooring-sydney/">Commercial flooring</a><a href="/builder-flooring-contractor-sydney/">Builder contractor</a><a href="/timber-floor-sanding-and-polishing-sydney/">Sanding and polishing</a><a href="/timber-floor-removal-and-stripping-sydney/">Removal and stripping</a></div></div><div><h3>Products</h3><div class="footer-links"><a href="/products/">Products</a><a href="/ranges/">All ranges</a><a href="/hybrid-flooring-sydney/">Hybrid</a><a href="/laminate-flooring-sydney/">Laminate</a><a href="/engineered-timber-flooring-sydney/">Engineered timber</a><a href="/solid-timber-flooring-sydney/">Solid timber</a><a href="/vinyl-flooring-sydney/">Vinyl</a></div></div><div><h3>Enquiries</h3><div class="footer-links"><a href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only">Request supply price</a><a href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install">Supply + install quote</a><a href="/contact/?enquiry=stock">Check stock availability</a><a href="/projects/">Projects</a><a href="/guides/">Guides</a><a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a><a href="/terms/">Terms</a></div></div></div><div class="shell footer-bottom">© 2026 Oz Timber Floor. Sydney timber flooring supply, installation and preparation.</