ss="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">12.0mm</span><span class="pill">15 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class="section" id="faqs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h2>Questions about Pantora Amor</h2></div></div><div class="faq-list"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Oz Timber Floor supply Pantora Amor without installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Send a supply-only enquiry with the preferred colour, quantity and suburb so stock, batch and lead time can be checked.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Pantora Amor be quoted with installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Include your suburb, approximate area, current floor and access details so preparation and installation scope can be reviewed.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Should I choose a colour before checking stock?</summary><div><p>You can shortlist colours first, but current stock, batch and product details should be confirmed before final ordering.</p></div></details></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Range enquiry</p><h2>Ready to ask about Pantora Amor?</h2><p>Send the range name, preferred colours, suburb, approximate area and whether you need supply-only, stock check or supply + install support.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Pantora+Amor&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fpantora-amor%2F">Request supply price</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Pantora+Amor&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fpantora-amor%2F">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Pantora+Amor&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fpantora-amor%2F">Supply + install</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class=