s%2Fprime-luxury-edition%2F">Ask about this range</a></div></div></section><section class="section soft catalogue-specs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Range snapshot</p><h2>Prime Luxury specifications</h2></div><p>Stock, batch, warranty and current product specifications are confirmed before order.</p></div><div class="spec-grid"><div class="spec-item"><span>Range</span><strong>Prime Luxury</strong></div><div class="spec-item"><span>Category</span><strong>Laminate</strong></div></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Project fit</p><h2>Best suited for</h2></div><p>Use these notes to decide whether this range belongs on your shortlist before checking colour, stock and installation details.</p></div><div class="fit-grid"><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Dry internal rooms</h3><p>A practical timber-look pathway for bedrooms, living areas and other suitable dry spaces.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Budget-aware renovations</h3><p>Useful for customers comparing appearance, availability and installation timing.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply-only enquiries</h3><p>Suitable when colour, quantity, trims and stock need confirmation before ordering.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply + install</h3><p>Useful when floor flatness, access and installation scope should be reviewed together.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Before ordering</p><h2>Confirm before ordering</h2></div><p>These checks help keep product choice, site conditions and installation expectations clear.</p></div><div class="caution-grid"><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Confirm</span>