tlist colours first, but current stock, batch and product details should be confirmed before final ordering.</p></div></details></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Range enquiry</p><h2>Ready to ask about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Aquastop 8mm?</h2><p>Send the range name, preferred colours, suburb, approximate area and whether you need supply-only, stock check or supply + install support.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Aquastop+8mm&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-aquastop-8mm%2F">Request supply price</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Aquastop+8mm&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-aquastop-8mm%2F">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Aquastop+8mm&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-aquastop-8mm%2F">Supply + install</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="shell footer-grid"><div><img class="footer-brand-logo" src="/assets/brand/oz-timber-floor-logo.webp" alt="Oz Timber Floor" width="680" height="215"><p>Sydney timber flooring supplier, installer, builder flooring contractor and floor preparation specialist.</p></div><div><h3>Services</h3><div class="footer-links"><a href="/timber-flooring-installation-