ent floor and access details so preparation and installation scope can be reviewed.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Should I choose a colour before checking stock?</summary><div><p>You can shortlist colours first, but current stock, batch and product details should be confirmed before final ordering.</p></div></details></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Range enquiry</p><h2>Ready to ask about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Contemporary?</h2><p>Send the range name, preferred colours, suburb, approximate area and whether you need supply-only, stock check or supply + install support.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Contemporary&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-contemporary-laminate%2F">Request supply price</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Contemporary&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-contemporary-laminate%2F">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Contemporary&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-contemporary-laminate%2F">Supply + install</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="shell footer-grid"><div><img class="footer-brand-logo" src="/assets/brand/oz-timber-floor