amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F"><strong>Check stock</strong><p>Already know the colour? Ask us to confirm current stock, batch and lead time.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="category-card link-card" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F"><strong>Request supply price</strong><p>For supply-only enquiries, include colour, quantity and suburb.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="category-card link-card" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F"><strong>Request supply + install quote</strong><p>For installed flooring, include area, current floor and access details.</p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class="section catalogue-products" id="colours"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Available colours</p><h2>Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan colours</h2></div><p>Open a colour page for product details, or check stock directly from the colour card.</p></div><div class="card missing-range-data"><h3>Colour list to confirm</h3><p>Ask Oz Timber Floor for the current colour list, samples and stock availability for this range.</p><a class="card-link" href="/contact/?enquiry=product&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Ask about this range</a></div></div></section><section class="section soft catalogue-specs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Range snapshot</p><h2>Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan specifications</h2></div><p>Stock, batch, warranty and current product specifications are confirmed before order.</p></div><div class="spec-grid"><div class="spec-item"><span>Range</span><strong>Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan</strong></div><div class="spec-item"><span>Category</span><strong>Laminate</strong></div></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Project fit</p><h2>Best suited for</h2></div><p>Use these notes to decide whether this range belongs on your shortlist before checking colour, stock and installation details.</p></div><div class="fit-grid"><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Dry internal rooms</h3><p>A practical timber-look pathway for bedrooms, living areas and other suitable dry spaces.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Budget-aware renovations</h3><p>Useful for customers comparing appearance, availability and installation timing.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply-only enquiries</h3><p>Suitable when colour, quantity, trims and stock need confirmation before ordering.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply + install</h3><p>Useful when floor flatness, access and installation scope should be reviewed together.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Before ordering</p><h2>Confirm before ordering</h2></div><p>These checks help keep product choice, site conditions and installation expectations clear.</p></div><div class="caution-grid"><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Confirm</span><h3>Stock and batch</h3><p>Confirm current availability, batch and lead time before payment or installation planning.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Review</span><h3>Floor condition</h3><p>Review subfloor flatness, moisture and stability before installation.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Plan</span><h3>Trims and transitions</h3><p>Check doorways, adjoining floors, skirting, scotia and expansion requirements.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Check</span><h3>Project suitability</h3><p>Some rooms, site conditions or usage types may need supplier or installer confirmation first.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Range help</p><h2>Need help choosing this range?</h2></div><p>Send your preferred colours, suburb, approximate floor area, current floor type and any photos or plans. Oz Timber Floor can help confirm stock, preparation and installation suitability before you order.</p></div><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Check stock</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Request supply + install quote</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=service&amp;topic=preparation&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Ask about preparation</a></div><p class="section-action">Not sure about floor levels? <a href="/floor-levelling-sydney/">Read about floor levelling in Sydney</a>.</p></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Related ranges</p><h2>Compare nearby options</h2></div><p>These ranges sit in the same broad flooring category.</p></div><div class="grid-3"><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/aqua-wood-plus-12mm/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/aqua-wood-plus-12mm/big-ben-ph.jpg" alt="Aqua Wood Plus 12mm laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>Aqua Wood Plus 12mm</h3><p>Aqua Wood Plus 12mm is a 12.0mm laminate range for customers comparing timber-look flooring for dry internal rooms and renovation budgets.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">12.0mm</span><span class="pill">24 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/aquastop-laminate/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/engineered-timber/hardwood-collection/zermatt/zermatt-swatch.webp" alt="Aquastop Laminate laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>Aquastop Laminate</h3><p>Aquastop Laminate is a laminate range for customers comparing timber-look flooring for dry internal rooms and renovation budgets.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">1 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/aquatuff-flooring/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/etf-aquatuff-flooring/acacia.jpg" alt="ETF Aquatuff Flooring laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>ETF Aquatuff Flooring</h3><p>ETF Aquatuff Flooring is a laminate flooring range for dry internal rooms where colour choice, stock timing and trim details should be confirmed before order.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">12.3mm</span><span class="pill">15 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/classic-laminate/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/floors/classic-laminate/classic-antique-oak/classic-antique-oak-swatch.webp" alt="Classic Laminate laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>Classic Laminate</h3><p>A classic laminate range for timber-look residential flooring enquiries.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">9 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/etf-1-5-meter-laminate/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/etf-1-5-meter-laminate/coastal-blackbutt-1-5m.jpg" alt="ETF 1.5 meter Laminate laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>ETF 1.5 meter Laminate</h3><p>ETF 1.5 meter Laminate is a laminate flooring range for dry internal rooms where colour choice, stock timing and trim details should be confirmed before order.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">8 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/etf-12mm-laminate/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/etf-12mm-laminate/aspen-oak.jpeg" alt="ETF 12mm Laminate laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>ETF 12mm Laminate</h3><p>ETF 12mm Laminate is a laminate flooring range for dry internal rooms where colour choice, stock timing and trim details should be confirmed before order.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">12.0mm</span><span class="pill">15 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class="section" id="faqs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h2>Questions about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan</h2></div></div><div class="faq-list"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Oz Timber Floor supply Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan without installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Send a supply-only enquiry with the preferred colour, quantity and suburb so stock, batch and lead time can be checked.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan be quoted with installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Include your suburb, approximate area, current floor and access details so preparation and installation scope can be reviewed.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Should I choose a colour before checking stock?</summary><div><p>You can shortlist colours first, but current stock, batch and product details should be confirmed before final ordering.</p></div></details></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Range enquiry</p><h2>Ready to ask about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Cosmopolitan?</h2><p>Send the range name, preferred colours, suburb, approximate area and whether you need supply-only, stock check or supply + install support.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Request supply price</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Cosmopolitan&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-cosmopolitan-laminate%2F">Supply + install</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="shell footer-grid"><div><img class="footer-brand-logo" src="/assets/brand/oz-timber-floor