amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Country&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-country-laminate%2F">Ask about this range</a></div></div></section><section class="section soft catalogue-specs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Range snapshot</p><h2>Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Country specifications</h2></div><p>Stock, batch, warranty and current product specifications are confirmed before order.</p></div><div class="spec-grid"><div class="spec-item"><span>Range</span><strong>Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Country</strong></div><div class="spec-item"><span>Category</span><strong>Laminate</strong></div></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Project fit</p><h2>Best suited for</h2></div><p>Use these notes to decide whether this range belongs on your shortlist before checking colour, stock and installation details.</p></div><div class="fit-grid"><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Dry internal rooms</h3><p>A practical timber-look pathway for bedrooms, living areas and other suitable dry spaces.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Budget-aware renovations</h3><p>Useful for customers comparing appearance, availability and installation timing.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply-only enquiries</h3><p>Suitable when colour, quantity, trims and stock need confirmation before ordering.</p></article><article class="fit-card"><span class="insight-label">Fit</span><h3>Supply + install</h3><p>Useful when floor flatness, access and installation scope should be reviewed together.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Before ordering</p><h2>Confirm before ordering</h2></div><p>These checks help keep product choice, site conditions and installation expectations clear.</p></div><div class="caution-grid"><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Confirm</span><h3>Stock and batch</h3><p>Confirm current availability, batch and lead time before payment or installation planning.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Review</span><h3>Floor condition</h3><p>Review subfloor flatness, moisture and stability before installation.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Plan</span><h3>Trims and transitions</h3><p>Check doorways, adjoining floors, skirting, scotia and expansion requirements.</p></article><article class="caution-card"><span class="insight-label">Check</span><h3>Project suitability</h3><p>Some rooms, site conditions or usage types may need supplier or installer confirmation first.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Range help</p><h2>Need help choosing this range?</h2></div><p>Send your preferred colours, suburb, approximate floor area, current floor type and any photos or plans. Oz Timber Floor can help confirm stock, preparation and installation suitability before you order.</p></div><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Country&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-country-laminate%2F">Check stock</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%