ooms where colour choice, stock timing and trim details should be confirmed before order.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">8 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="card range-summary-card link-card" href="/ranges/etf-12mm-laminate/"><img class="category-thumb" src="/assets/products/laminate/etf-12mm-laminate/aspen-oak.jpeg" alt="ETF 12mm Laminate laminate colour swatch" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><p class="catalogue-overline">Laminate</p><h3>ETF 12mm Laminate</h3><p>ETF 12mm Laminate is a laminate flooring range for dry internal rooms where colour choice, stock timing and trim details should be confirmed before order.</p><p class="product-meta"><span class="pill">Laminate</span><span class="pill">12.0mm</span><span class="pill">15 colours</span></p><span class="card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class="section" id="faqs"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h2>Questions about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Heritage</h2></div></div><div class="faq-list"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Oz Timber Floor supply Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Heritage without installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Send a supply-only enquiry with the preferred colour, quantity and suburb so stock, batch and lead time can be checked.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Heritage be quoted with installation?</summary><div><p>Yes. Include your suburb, approximate area, current floor and access details so preparation and installation scope can be reviewed.</p></div></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Should I choose a colour before checking stock?</summary><div><p>You can shortlist colours first, but current stock, batch and product details should be confirmed before final ordering.</p></div></details></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell cta"><p class="eyebrow">Range enquiry</p><h2>Ready to ask about Villeroy &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Boch Heritage?</h2><p>Send the range name, preferred colours, suburb, approximate area and whether you need supply-only, stock check or supply + install support.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-only&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Heritage&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-heritage-laminate%2F">Request supply price</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=stock&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Heritage&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-heritage-laminate%2F">Check stock availability</a><a class="button-secondary" href="/contact/?enquiry=supply-install&amp;range=Villeroy+%26amp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3Bamp%3B+Boch+Heritage&amp;category=Laminate&amp;source=%2Franges%2Fvilleroy-boch-heritage-laminate%2F">Supply + install</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="shell footer-grid"><div><img class="footer-brand-logo" src="/assets/brand/oz-timber-floor-logo.webp" alt="Oz Timber Floor" width="680" height="215"><p>Sydney timber flooring supplier, installer, builder flooring contractor and floor preparation specialist.</p><